REQUIREMENTS
{p} {p}
NewsRog requires:
{p} {p}
   o  MUI 3.8 or later{p}
   o  8 Mb RAM & 8 Mb HD (more recommended){p}
   o  AmiTCP, Miami, or other compatible networking software{p}
   o  A 68020 or faster CPU (68040+ recommended)
{p} {p}
Only the Amiga version is available at this time.